title: 10 More Books - May 2015 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 more books for this month. 9 ePUBs & 1 MOBI. Covers included in saparate folder:

01. American General - The Life and Times of William Tecumseh Sherman
02. Behind Every Great Man - The Forgotten Women Behind the World's Famous and Infamous
03. Dear Cary - My Life with Cary Grant
04. Handcraft EPUB In 7 Steps
05. Llewellyn's Complete Dictionary of Dreams - Over 1,000 Dream Symbols and Their Universal Meanings
06. Routledge Handbook of Communication Disorders
07. The ABCs of Property Management - What You Need to Know to Maximize Your Money Now, Second Edition
08. The Accidental Feminist - The Life of One Woman through War, Motherhood, and International Photojournalism
09. The Lucky Santangelo Cookbook
10. What Are You Looking At - The Surprising, Shocking, and Sometimes Strange Story of 150 Years of Modern Art
